Description: Feature-rich screenshot application
 Shutter is a feature-rich screenshot program. 
 You can take a screenshot of a specific area, window, your whole screen, 
 or even of a website - apply different effects to it, draw on it to highlight points, 
 and then upload to a image hosting site, all within one window.
 .
 The Shutter homepage is http://launchpad.net/shutter
